text: I was at Clementi branch today and I expected to wait long but wait time was very short. I needed a cashiers order urgently, and was Served within 5mins by a kind-hearted friendly lady Noraini on the second floor who was very kind and helpful and efficient. Got my cashier order within 5minutes. Thank you for the efficiency and your willingness to help , your kind demeanour really made my day and was  great relief to a stressful dayüòÅüòÅ

Went there to open a savings account account (foreigner), better to queue 10-15mins ahead. Staff was friendly but seems their laptop was too old and system was too slow, I ended up there almost two hours to wait until they finish the process (and still need to wait for a week for approval, activating your account in person again)

I had a great experience at UOB Bank recently, thanks to the excellent service provided by Wincy Kong. She was professional, friendly, and handled my request efficiently. Her positive attitude and prompt assistance made the whole process smooth and pleasant. I truly appreciate her dedication and hope to receive such outstanding service again in the future!

I was at this branch yesterday and was served by Ms Noraini.
She was pleasant and efficient.  She never seemed to get flustered and steadily completed the 2 transactions I had to do without any difficulties. She knows her work well. Her pleasant demeanour and kind personality make it a pleasure to deal with her.
Wishing her the best in her career and congratulating UOB for having such a wonderful staff.

My colleague wanted to sign up a credit card for our corporate account, came before lunch but was told the only person in charge was not ard, was asked to come back, came back at 3pm the person was busy with 1 customer waited for 40min, when the person in charge is free, her told duty over, asked her to go IMM as it opens till 630pm, i was shock by the lousy service, so irresponsible
